lyrics:
[Verse]
Oliwia, Julka, and Adriane in a Skoda Fabia ride
With us and our cats, Kociczka and Absurd by their side
We're cruising down the road, feeling the breeze
Together in harmony, we're having the best of ease

[Chorus]
Oh, Oliwia, Julka, and Adriane, let the music play
In our Skoda Fabia, we'll enjoy the ride every day
Kociczka and Absurd, our feline friends so dear
We'll make memories together, spreading love and cheer
